title: ARIA Awards 2015 + Red Carpet Special PDTV.x264-KCRT
description:
Aria Awards 2015




Red Carpet: Join Scott Tweedie and Olivia Phyland hosting the arrivals at The ARIA Red Carpet By David Jones, while Angela Bishop and Joel Creasey cover all things fashion as well as some exclusive interviews!


Hosted by Osher Gunsberg, tune in for the biggest ARIAs ceremony in years. With a plethora of Australian and international acts descending on Sydney to celebrate the most outstanding music of 2015




Original Air Date: 26-Nov-2015
